---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navigation from "../components/Navigation.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";

import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Layout title="Education — SUTD Cleanroom" description="Hands-on cleanroom education for undergraduate and postgraduate students at SUTD.">
  <Navigation />

  <main class="pt-24 pb-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Back link -->
      <a href="/sutd-cleanroom/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-text-primary transition-colors mb-8">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
        </svg>
        Back to Home
      </a>

      <!-- Hero -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block text-xs font-semibold text-accent uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Education</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight">
          Hands-On Cleanroom<br />Experience for Undergraduates
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
          At SUTD, the cleanroom is not just a facility for research. It is a place where education becomes real &mdash; where students connect classroom concepts with actual fabrication, and where early exposure can spark future research ideas and deep-tech ambitions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Photo gallery -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-16" id="education-gallery">
        <div class="col-span-2 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border">
          <img src="/sutd-cleanroom/images/education/hero.jpg" alt="Wide view of students in the SUTD Cleanroom" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-[2/1]" loading="eager" />
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border">
          <img src="/sutd-cleanroom/images/education/workshop-01.jpg" alt="Students gathered around equipment" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-[3/4]" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border">
          <img src="/sutd-cleanroom/images/education/workshop-02.jpg" alt="Cleanroom briefing session" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-[3/4]" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border">
          <img src="/sutd-cleanroom/images/education/workshop-03.jpg" alt="Students observing demonstration" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-[3/4]" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border">
          <img src="/sutd-cleanroom/images/education/workshop-04.jpg" alt="Equipment walkthrough" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-[3/4]" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border">
          <img src="/sutd-cleanroom/images/education/workshop-05.jpg" alt="Students learning about deposition" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-[3/4]" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border">
          <img src="/sutd-cleanroom/images/education/workshop-06.jpg" alt="Lithography demonstration" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-[3/4]" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border">
          <img src="/sutd-cleanroom/images/education/workshop-07.jpg" alt="Safety protocols briefing" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-[3/4]" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-2 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border">
          <img src="/sutd-cleanroom/images/education/workshop-10.jpg" alt="Hands-on session with students" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-[2/1]" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border">
          <img src="/sutd-cleanroom/images/education/workshop-08.jpg" alt="Chemical storage walkthrough" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-[3/4]" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border">
          <img src="/sutd-cleanroom/images/education/workshop-09.jpg" alt="Students in cleanroom gowns" class="w-full h-full object-cover aspect-[3/4]" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose-content max-w-3xl">

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">What Happens When Undergraduates Step Into a Cleanroom?</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
          They stop seeing chips and devices as mysterious black boxes, and start wondering how they can build them themselves.
        </p>

        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We recently hosted a broader cohort of undergraduates at the SUTD Cleanroom for a hands-on introduction to cleanroom work. They were briefed on cleanroom safety and protocols, introduced to substrate preparation, and walked through the basics of lithography, etching, and thin-film processes.
        </p>

        <!-- What students experienced -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4 mt-12">What Students Experienced</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-surface-card border border-border rounded-xl p-5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">Safety & Protocols</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-text-secondary">Cleanroom safety briefing, gowning procedures, and contamination control</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface-card border border-border rounded-xl p-5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.75 3.104v5.714a2.25 2.25 0 01-.659 1.591L5 14.5M9.75 3.104c-.251.023-.501.05-.75.082m.75-.082a24.301 24.301 0 014.5 0m0 0v5.714c0 .597.237 1.17.659 1.591L19.8 15.3M14.25 3.104c.251.023.501.05.75.082M19.8 15.3l-1.57.393A9.065 9.065 0 0112 15a9.065 9.065 0 00-6.23.693L5 14.5m14.8.8l1.402 1.402c1.232 1.232.65 3.318-1.067 3.611A48.309 48.309 0 0112 21c-2.773 0-5.491-.235-8.135-.687-1.718-.293-2.3-2.379-1.067-3.61L5 14.5" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">Substrate Preparation</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-text-secondary">Introduction to wafer handling, cleaning, and preparation techniques</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface-card border border-border rounded-xl p-5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M2.036 12.322a1.012 1.012 0 010-.639C3.423 7.51 7.36 4.5 12 4.5c4.638 0 8.573 3.007 9.963 7.178.07.207.07.431 0 .639C20.577 16.49 16.64 19.5 12 19.5c-4.638 0-8.573-3.007-9.963-7.178z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">Equipment Demos</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-text-secondary">Live demos of spin coater, e-beam evaporator, and mask aligner</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface-card border border-border rounded-xl p-5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M21 7.5l-9-5.25L3 7.5m18 0l-9 5.25m9-5.25v9l-9 5.25M3 7.5l9 5.25M3 7.5v9l9 5.25m0-9v9" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">Hands-On Fabrication</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-text-secondary">EBL-fabricated samples under the microscope and wire-bonded devices</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
          What stayed with us most was their reaction. By the end of the visit, many of them were already asking: <span class="text-text-primary font-medium italic">when can we start our own projects?</span> That excitement is exactly why experiences like this matter.
        </p>

        <!-- Quote highlight -->
        <div class="border-l-4 border-accent bg-accent/5 rounded-r-xl p-6 my-10">
          <p class="text-text-primary font-medium leading-relaxed">
            This is how future builders begin &mdash; by seeing, touching, and experiencing the process for themselves.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Acknowledgements -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4 mt-12">Acknowledgements</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
          A big thank you to the team who guided students through the experience:
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
          <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-surface-card border border-border text-text-primary font-medium">John Chan</span>
          <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-surface-card border border-border text-text-primary font-medium">Sethu Narayanan Tamilselvan</span>
          <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-surface-card border border-border text-text-primary font-medium">Budiman Salam</span>
          <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-surface-card border border-border text-text-primary font-medium">Md. Abdur Rahman</span>
          <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-surface-card border border-border text-text-primary font-medium">Deepshikha Arora</span>
          <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-surface-card border border-border text-text-primary font-medium">Rou Yun Teo</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          We would also like to thank <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Prof. Joel Yang</span> for driving this broader initiative and for helping shape the cleanroom as a space for education, hands-on learning, and future deep-tech building.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
